      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) says that approval has been given for 3-Hour power cuts for the 21st of July as follows;",
        "IMF hopes to complete Sri Lanka aid talks \u2018as quickly as possible\u2019"
